name: VESTIDO SHOP SEÑAL
campo_seis:
Black satin cocktail dress embellished with red and white sequins.

Featuring a traffic inspired "shop" sign on the chest, and a figure-enhancing knee length design.

This dress is from Moschino´s SS16 runway capsule collection.
